installing expo in your system:
D:\Workspaces\ReactNative>npm install -g expo-cli

Create account in https://expo.io/
D:\Workspaces\ReactNative>expo login

D:\Workspaces\ReactNative>expo init confusion

open folder in visual code 
D:\Workspaces\ReactNative>code .	

D:\Workspaces\ReactNative\confusion>npm start	

Download Expo app in mobile:
scan QR code it's building JS bundles and start working...

Setup GIT repo:
goto GitHub -> create new repo 'ReactNative'

vkamaliy@LIN64015861 MINGW64 /d/Workspaces/ReactNative/confusion (master)
$ git init

D:\Workspaces\ReactNative\confusion>npm install react-native-elements
